Does anyone know what could be happening?

The ibflowbin I used was at:
https://dogfood.instabase.com/apps/flow/run/ib_eng/tests/fs/Test%20Drive/tests/general/multiflows/custom_posthook/build/bin/flows-2019-12-16-16:44:54.ibflowbin
